Author’s Note: This seventh story has elements from Hope and Sabby’s challenges, V’s story arc challenge, and has a mention of something that Blue asked for.  As usual, the requirements will be listed at the end.  By the way, if you didn’t know already, I’m looking for further challenges for this series – so feel free to email them to me.  This one starts right where the last one left off.<br>
