Story 7: Motherly Love - Chapter 4<br>
<br>
~*~*~*~*~*~<br>
<br>
“Why would you automatically jump to *that* conclusion?” Chloe asked in an angry, insulted tone, her hands placed firmly on her hips.<br>
<br>
Mr. Mxyzptlk smiled evilly at Clark as he folded his small arms smugly across his chest.<br>
<br>
“Yes, Clark, do tell,” he said, every note of his voice tweaked with utter delight.  “What could have possibly made you think that the little blonde girl is an alien?” <br>
<br>
